				I do suggest doing the Polar Bear quest. Only takes one skin to do, give it to Cindl in Mac's Kilts, she'll give you 1 gp and a peice of patchwork armor, and very nice exp (for low levels anyways).  If your lookin for money from the pelts dont just sell them to a vendor, you'll get more money by doing this quest and selling the armor that you get.<BR>
